window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>This box set contains </b><b><i>Requiem of the Soul</i></b><b>, </b><b><i>Reparation of Sin</i></b><b>, and </b><b><i>Resurrection of the Heart</i></b><b> and tells the complete story of Santiago De La Rosa and Ivy Moreno!</b></p> <p>I was born with noble blood in my veins. Heir to a powerful dynasty. Wealth. Power. Aristocracy. Temptations too dangerous to resist. Until someone tried to steal it all. Scarred and broken, I emerged from the flames.</p> <p>Now I’ve returned to take what’s mine. Revenge.</p> <p>The first item on my agenda? Make Ivy Moreno my wife.</p> <p>Second? Bend her until she breaks.</p>"; 
